0efbcc740572b37847a5e8bade4d088b  alpine.patch"
sha256sums="d01bee43c6df79f7bbc1149bb3e85f489491fb2358a6a1f9a7f0d6e07715832f  pypy2-v5.7.1-src.tar.bz2
